'''Amlulli n unebdu''' neɣ [[amud n tlemmast n unebdu]] d alfay (d aneḍru) [[tallunt|anallun]] mi ara ad tili [[tizgelt tarakalt]] i wezgen n kra n [[itrikli|umtiweg]] (azgen n ugafa neɣ n wenẓul) yedda ar [[itri|yitri]] i yeṭṭafar, Deg [[tagnit|tegnit]] deg [[Amlulli n unebdu|umlulli n unebdu]] yettili [[akennaw agellusan|ukennaw-is]] n [[tagnit|agellusan]] ɣer tseddaṛt tafellayt +23,44° (ɣef wannect-a [[asinef (tallunt'')|asinef n tfukt]] ɣef [[asebges agennaw|usebges agennaw]] yettili-d s wazal n +23,44° deg wezgen n ugafa yakk d -23,44° deg wezgen n wenẓul) anect-a yettili-d snat n tikkal deg useggas (tikkelt i yal azgen n tegnit)

== Iylan ==
Mya (madam) deg umlulli n unebdu yettili-d deg [[Azal (akud)|wazal]] meqqren yakk izmaz n [[akud|wakud]] n [[alluy|walluy n tafukt]] id yettasen yakk zik d [[aɣelluy|uɣelluy n tfukt]] iy smezgaren (ṭṭewwilen) s wazal n kra n wussan, Ayen id yesnummken d akken mači s umsefki ad yili walluy id yettasen yakk zik deg umlulli n unebdu

